# ANSVK Constitution

## Brief introduction
This is the top-level non-negotiable rule set for AI-assisted development in this repo. It aligns architecture, data, and UI decisions so generated code remains consistent and maintainable.

- Stack: Flutter + Riverpod + go_router
- Source of truth for UI tokens: DB-first process, generated token code in `lib/ui/tokens/`
- Prefer feature-first structure under `lib/features/`
- Do not create parallel design systems or duplicate component families
- Keep security basics: no secrets in git, no credentials in source files
